{"tid":1667792,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"稱警選擇性道歉屬歧視 天主教徒入稟索償","createTime":"2019-10-21T15:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T17:08:22.000Z","uid":193217,"like":75,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"0a6cd1045e2acfeda71ff329e2814284c2c68e10","tid":1667792,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:55:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191021/mobile/bkn-20191021165912768-1021_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20191021%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20191021165912768-1021_00822_001.html&d=bp2T%2F%2B5c5q8hcpZmRI3qNr9ZTfDhdyQuSOQsORMTmv0%3D&h=17abc0bf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20191021/mobile/bkn-20191021165912768-1021_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n稱警選擇性道歉屬歧視 天主教徒入稟索償<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥與警務處處長盧偉聰今(21日)到尖沙咀清真寺，就昨天(20日)警方水炮車向清真寺噴射藍色水柱，將清真寺染藍一事道歉。有報稱是天主教信徒的前法庭書記指，警方近期執法活動，屢次褻瀆不同宗教，但只選擇向穆斯林團體道歉，對其他宗教團體是歧視性待遇，有感傷害。他今入稟小額錢債審裁處向警務處處長追討5000港元賠償，案件押至12月10日進行聆訊。<br />\n<br />\n申索人譚志輝，被告人是警務處處長。譚稱，警方在反修例示威中的執法，曾有警員威嚇牧師、說「叫耶穌落嚟見我」和包圍灣仔循道衞理香港堂。警方一直沒有向天主教及基督教作出道歉，卻選擇性向伊斯蘭教道歉，認為警方歧視所有香港天主教及基督教的教友，包括他本人，疑違反《香港人權法案條例》，故向警務處處長造成的「情感傷害」索償5000港元，並要求處長向香港教區道歉。<br />\n<br />\n據知，譚今早曾致電平等機會委員會，就本事情作投訴，惟遭平機會拒絕受理。"},{"pid":"3c7d3318665c7a25884035f6cde6d6960e0d6ee1","tid":1667792,"uid":193217,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:55:56.000Z","msg":"咪係.林鄭大細超<br />\n天主教就唔洗理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點對得住蘇哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇連登仔準備咁玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0e5aca923686f0f65dd88a522c5aa5fbbb71ae2","tid":1667792,"uid":172306,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:56:47.000Z","msg":"全港基督徒應該分別入稟"},{"pid":"bb65928ed5aba23ba66a3a2e7ae818b650834ad3","tid":1667792,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:56:50.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"b82dcd40c42a46c9015ee420b16c02ce1de318c6","tid":1667792,"uid":193217,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:58:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVh5Pne.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVh5Pne.jpg&h=794a09d4&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n蘇哥就唔係神?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n林鄭你信咩嫁"},{"pid":"6fc8e04bd795bdb6035e88b8979e63c0503ef352","tid":1667792,"uid":193217,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:58:58.000Z","msg":"「神是妒忌的神」<br />\n&quot;除了我以外，你不可有別的神。&quot;<br />\n出埃及記20:3<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲話天堂有個位留比佢<br />\n落地獄啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31861af10c117dd98908875baf6d79bc1996f766","tid":1667792,"uid":193217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass